metadata.description:
theDOLOSproject : The Pilot

-The term "PILOT" in television represents a prototype of the upcoming series; a standalone episode setting the tone of what is to come next. If approved, the show continues. 

THIS is the pilot. 

Becoming the owner of this piece comes with great power - you can hold or sell the token, or burn it in exchange for a custom DOLOS piece that will be minted into the collection.
